>Description:
A second click on bug icon causes exit dialog to appear. It is necessary
to click the buttons (Exit button don't closes DrScheme) to dismiss the dialog and to see the backtrace window.
>How-To-Repeat:
Evaluate the following expression into the Interactions window and click
the bug icon, close the backtrace window and click the bug icon again.

(/ 1 0)
